    <!-- ═══ APP-SPECIFIC FAQ ════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 border-y-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-primary/15 dark:bg-primary/5" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
        <header class="mb-10 text-center">
          <h2 id="faq-heading" class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm">The most common questions about using the gikomba.app.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="space-y-3">

          <details class="group border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]" open>
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 list-none gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">How do I pay for items using M-Pesa?</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-ink-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm leading-relaxed">
              When you find an item you want to buy, tap "Buy Now" and follow the M-Pesa STK push on your phone. Your payment is held securely by gikomba.app until you confirm the item has arrived as described — then it's released to the seller.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 list-none gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">How do I list an item for sale on the app?</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-ink-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Tap the + button on the home screen, take up to 8 photos, fill in a description and price, then tap "List Item". Your listing is live immediately and visible to buyers across Nairobi.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 list-none gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Is my money safe if something goes wrong?</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-ink-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Yes. All payments are held in escrow by gikomba.app until you confirm receipt. If the item doesn't arrive or isn't as described, you can open a dispute within the app and we'll review it within 24 hours.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 list-none gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">How do I get a Verified Seller badge?</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-ink-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Go to your profile settings and tap "Verify Account". You'll be asked to upload a photo of your ID. Verification takes up to 2 hours and unlocks the seller badge, boosting your listing visibility.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A]">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 list-none gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Which cities does gikomba.app deliver to?</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-ink-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0">expand_more</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We support deliveries across Nairobi, Mombasa, Kisumu, Nakuru, and Eldoret. You can also arrange local meetups anywhere in Kenya. More cities coming soon.
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ CONTACT FORM ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-16 py-16 sm:py-24" id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Details -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <div>
            <h2 id="contact-heading" class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Still need help?</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
              Our Nairobi-based team is standing by. We reply within 24 hours on weekdays.
            </p>
          </div>
          <address class="not-italic flex flex-col gap-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-11 h-11 border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-accent/10 text-accent flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Email</h3>
                <a href="mailto:support@gikomba.app" class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark hover:text-secondary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors">support@gikomba.app</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-11 h-11 border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-secondary/10 text-secondary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">forum</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">In-App Chat</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">Mon–Fri, 8am–6pm EAT. Tap "Support" in the app menu.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-11 h-11 border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Office</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">Westlands Commercial Centre,<br />Ring Rd Parklands, Nairobi</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </address>
        </div>

        <!-- Form -->
        <div class="border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-white dark:bg-[#1A1A1A] p-7 sm:p-8" style="box-shadow:5px 5px 0 #111">
          <form class="flex flex-col gap-5" onsubmit="return false;">

            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                <label for="c-name" class="text-xs font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark uppercase tracking-widest">Name</label>
                <input id="c-name" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="Your name"
                  class="w-full border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#111] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors placeholder:text-ink-muted" />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                <label for="c-email" class="text-xs font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark uppercase tracking-widest">Email</label>
                <input id="c-email" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="you@example.com"
                  class="w-full border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#111] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors placeholder:text-ink-muted" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
              <label for="c-topic" class="text-xs font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark uppercase tracking-widest">Topic</label>
              <select id="c-topic"
                class="w-full border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#111] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors">
                <option>M-Pesa / Payment Issue</option>
                <option>Listing Problem</option>
                <option>Delivery or Meetup</option>
                <option>Account / Verification</option>
                <option>Report a Seller</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
              <label for="c-msg" class="text-xs font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark uppercase tracking-widest">Message</label>
              <textarea id="c-msg" rows="4" placeholder="Describe your issue..."
                class="w-full border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#111] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors resize-none placeholder:text-ink-muted"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit"
              class="w-full bg-secondary text-white font-bold py-4 border-2 border-ink dark:border-[#444] text-sm hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] hover:[box-shadow:none] transition-all"
              style="box-shadow:4px 4px 0 #111">
              Send Message
            </button>

          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

